latestPosts.caption:
Every title he holds is not just an accolade, but a story of determination, discipline, and undeniable charm.
Presenting one of the most charismatic faces in the world of pageantry —
Prateek Thapa, crowned GMI Mr. India and IAMS International 2024.
From the ramp to reality, his journey is a blend of passion, precision, and purpose.
With every step, he’s inspired confidence. With every win, he’s defined excellence.
As he takes his seat on the jury panel of Mr. & Miss Baisakhi 2025,
he brings not just experience, but a vision — to spot the spark, the story, and the soul behind every contestant.
A mentor, a model, and a man of impeccable grace —
Prateek Thapa is here to celebrate elegance in its truest form.
